{"tid":1021554,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[做好人做好事] 一年前約定粉絲「IU到學校看我」　她真的來畢業典禮！全場嚇傻","createTime":"2019-02-14T10:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T16:29:32.000Z","uid":34643,"like":445,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"471422940d926796e8cf9c960f469d3384d489c7","tid":1021554,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_dafba704297ecef97844493ad1183d5e/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-14/113954-705797.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_dafba704297ecef97844493ad1183d5e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-14%2F113954-705797.jpg&h=d93e6cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實力寵粉的IU！<br />\n<br />\n今日（2月14日），IU遠赴位於全羅北道的金堤女子高中，出席了該校的畢業典禮。 IU出席是因為該校的1位高中生Uaena在十周年FM上，請求IU出席她們學校的畢業典禮。 所以IU今日來給她實現願望了。<br />\n<br />\nIU為全校畢業生準備了畢業禮物：「叫做香雪蘭的花，花語是為妳的啟程應援。 」為了這位Uaena，IU還準備了特別的禮物：「因為是她邀請我的，所以特別地準備了花束。 還問了身邊年輕朋友畢業禮物送什麽好，說是香水。 所以選了我個人非常喜歡的身體乳和香水。 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DzV0WseU0AEzaOA.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDzV0WseU0AEzaOA.jpg%3Aorig&h=8f4b1111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨後IU準備離場，學生們呼喊安可。 IU就說：「我自己來的，沒來得及帶伴舞來，可以再唱1首嗎？ 」學生們當然求之不得。 IU：「穿成這樣跳《BBIBBI》，會不會很奇怪？ 」學生們：「不會！ 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a62b060bb8864027cce47d4700abc362/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-14/113954-705801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a62b060bb8864027cce47d4700abc362%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-14%2F113954-705801.jpg&h=d374608a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如此整個過程是演唱了《你的意義》+談話+《BBIBBI》，IU還可愛地忘詞了&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/egrE9RJweo0?t=69\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FegrE9RJweo0%3Ft%3D69&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDoLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=c7df0238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/egrE9RJweo0?t=69</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mimgnews.pstatic.net/image/009/2019/02/14/0004304302_002_20190214142106211.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmimgnews.pstatic.net%2Fimage%2F009%2F2019%2F02%2F14%2F0004304302_002_20190214142106211.jpg&h=45766ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3084a1cc6e8a015f1bdbddaf94ee74cb/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-14/113954-705800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3084a1cc6e8a015f1bdbddaf94ee74cb%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-14%2F113954-705800.jpg&h=99870b54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdd60ea43ca66168966ae104f127e44aea34ab70","tid":1021554,"uid":79382,"like":87,"dislike":2,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:25:31.000Z","msg":"好善良 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23064b51a23288a3a2f60d04be56140dcdcadec","tid":1021554,"uid":56649,"like":5,"dislike":72,"score":-67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:25:32.000Z","msg":"iu打算幾時實現同我結婚的約定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa61e5b11c4d6ccdff05cb0494b96699714c444c","tid":1021554,"uid":79382,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"e23064b51a23288a3a2f60d04be56140dcdcadec","tid":1021554,"uid":56649,"like":5,"dislike":72,"score":-67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:25:32.000Z","msg":"iu打算幾時實現同我結婚的約定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:25:56.000Z","msg":"走啦<br />\nIU我㗎"},{"pid":"60ae6e4591441088325634120578d6e5ec92db49","tid":1021554,"uid":219225,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"好感動 哭左"},{"pid":"b965ab6ccab1bc6d14f757f1a73c0c7e3977d66e","tid":1021554,"uid":